OL,3,CUK to host Hormuz planning meeting as
OL,4,CTrump deadline looms for Iran
OL,6,FBritain will host a meeting of allied
OL,7,Fmilitary officers to discuss plans for
OL,8,Fsecuring the Strait of Hormuz as
OL,9,FDonald Trump's deadline for Iran to
OL,10,Freopen the waterway looms.
OL,12,FThe US president has given Tehran
OL,13,Funtil 8pm on Tuesday Washington time
OL,14,F(1am on Wednesday UK time) to end its
OL,15,Fblockade of the strait or be bombed
OL,16,F"back to the Stone Ages".
