OL,3,CUK to host Hormuz planning meeting as
OL,4,CTrump deadline looms for Iran
OL,6,FAt a press conference on Monday, Mr
OL,7,FTrump reiterated his threat to attack
OL,8,FIran's civilian infrastructure,
OL,9,Fincluding power plants and bridges,
OL,10,Fdismissing the suggestion that such
OL,11,Factions would constitute a war crime.
OL,13,FThe UK Government has pledged to stay
OL,14,Fout of any offensive action against
OL,15,FIran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
