OL,3,CUK to host Hormuz planning meeting as
OL,4,CTrump deadline looms for Iran
OL,6,FAhead of Tuesday's deadline, Britain's
OL,7,FPermanent Joint Headquarters at
OL,8,FNorthwood, outside London, will host a
OL,9,Fmeeting of military planners to
OL,10,Fdiscuss long-term measures to secure
OL,11,Fthe Strait of Hormuz.
OL,13,FThe strait, a vital shipping route for
OL,14,Foil and gas, has been effectively
OL,15,Fblockaded by Tehran since the outbreak
OL,16,Fof war, causing major disruption to
OL,17,Foil supplies and threatening fuel
OL,18,Fshortages across the world.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
