OL,3,CUK to host Hormuz planning meeting as
OL,4,CTrump deadline looms for Iran
OL,6,FTuesday's meeting is expected to focus
OL,7,Fon plans for an international
OL,8,Fcoalition to make the strait safe for
OL,9,Fshipping once hostilities have ended.
OL,11,FIt follows a meeting of more than 40
OL,12,Fnations, chaired by Foreign Secretary
OL,13,FYvette Cooper, that discussed
OL,14,Fcollective action to increase pressure
OL,15,Fon Tehran to reopen Hormuz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
