OL,3,CUK to host Hormuz planning meeting as
OL,4,CTrump deadline looms for Iran
OL,6,FBut no deployment is likely to take
OL,7,Fplace until Iran, America and Israel
OL,8,Fhave agreed a ceasefire, with the risk
OL,9,Fthat vessels would be hit by Iranian
OL,10,Fdrones or missiles currently deemed
OL,11,Ftoo high even by the US Navy.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, Mr Trump continued to pour
OL,14,Fscorn on Nato and the UK over their
OL,15,Frefusal to support offensive
OL,16,Foperations against Iran or agree to
OL,17,Fhis attempt to annex Greenland from
OL,18,FDenmark.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
