OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775523444
OL,3,CUK to host Hormuz planning meeting as
OL,4,CTrump deadline looms for Iran
OL,6,FDescribing the alliance as a "paper
OL,7,Ftiger" during Monday's press
OL,8,Fconference, the president added: "It
OL,9,Fall began with, if you want to know
OL,10,Fthe truth, Greenland.
OL,12,F"We want Greenland. They don't want to
OL,13,Fgive it to us. And I said, 'bye bye'."
OL,15,FEarlier, Mr Trump had renewed his
OL,16,Fpersonal criticism of Sir Keir
OL,17,FStarmer, appearing to compare the
OL,18,FPrime Minister to Neville Chamberlain,
OL,19,Fnow mostly remembered for his policy
OL,20,Fof appeasement towards Nazi Germany in
OL,21,Fthe 1930s.
